title: Minister Lamamra receives the new Ambassador of Azerbaijan to Algeria
text: The Minister of Foreign Affairs and National Community Abroad, Mr. Ramtane Lamamra, received Mr. Tural Anar oglu Rzayev, who handed him figurative copies of the Letters of Credence accrediting him as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of the Republic of Azerbaijan to People's Democratic Republic of Algeria.Â
